data.description: Fantastic 3 bed, 2 full bath all brick Ranch single family home. Spacious living room with hardwood floors throughout , formal dining room, eat-in kitchen with granite counter tops, double sinks plus lots of oak cabinets, ample closets with dressing mirrors. 3rd bedroom on the lower lever full finished basement that would be great for entertaining. 2 car garage with long side drive, fenced rear yard for summer gatherings, quite tree lined streets. Home is located among other well maintained home. Close to shopping, schools, library, public transportation and minutes from expressways.
